											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="A black sphere suddenly envelopes Shadowheart. She finds herself in a strange, dark nowhere. A black disc with a fringe of purple glow, almost like an eclipse, appears before her, forming Shar's symbol. Just barely visible within the disc is what appear to be a figure, arms outstretched to the sides, as if suspended from the disc itself.The wound on Shadowheart's hand glows as Shar speaks to her - only this time, she does not wince in pain. The wild, flickering magic slows and coalesces into a black magic sphere balanced upon her hand. She stares at it with awe and a little trepidation." />
										</node>
